# 🍳 TasteCraft

> **Cook → Design → Serve → Manage → Build Your Own Food Empire**

---

# 🌟 Core Idea

TasteCraft sirf cooking game nahi hai.

Ye ek complete food business simulation hai jahan player apna food empire bana sakta hai.

Player ban sakta hai:

- 👨‍🍳 Chef
- 🍔 Restaurant Owner
- ☕ Cafe Owner
- 🍰 Baker
- 🚚 Food Truck Owner
- 🌾 Farmer
- 🥛 Dairy Owner
- 🍣 Sushi Master

---

# 🏪 Restaurant System

## Restaurant Ownership

Player choose kar sakta hai:

- Employee
- Owner
- Co-Owner (Friends ke saath)

Roles:

- Chef
- Waiter
- Cashier
- Cleaner
- Manager
- Delivery Driver

---

## Restaurant Builder

Restaurant ko poori freedom ke saath design kar sakte ho.

- Multiple Floors
- Garden
- Fountain
- Stage
- Game Zone
- Gym
- Shops
- Decorations
- Interior Design
- Exterior Design

Open Kitchen / Closed Kitchen dono option.

---

# 👨‍🍳 Cooking System

Players:

- Recipe Book follow kar sakte hain
- Khud recipes invent kar sakte hain
- Signature Dish bana sakte hain
- Recipe Book unlock kar sakte hain

---

# 📖 Recipe Book

Har successful custom recipe automatically Recipe Book me save hogi.

---

# ⭐ Signature Dish

Player customize kar sakta hai:

- Dish Name
- Description
- Presentation

Restaurant ki special dish ban jayegi.

---

# 🌍 World Cuisine

Har country ki famous dishes.

Har state/province ki regional dishes.

---

# 🌾 Farming

Restaurant ke ingredients khud produce kar sakte ho.

Examples:

- Vegetables
- Fruits
- Wheat
- Rice
- Dairy
- Fish
- Meat

